    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Stemmed dessert glasses for serving various kinds of sweetmeats. Made in a variety of forms and styles, often following the fashions of contemporary drinking glasses. For dishes used for serving sweetmeats, use "sweetmeat dishes."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000099620/Legacy AAT data</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Copas de postre con pie para servir varias clases de confites. Hechas en una variedad de formas y estilos, a menudo siguiendo las modas de las copas contemporáneas para beber.  </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
